CERTAINLY ENJOYED IT.

30
00:04:11,451 --> 00:04:12,919
YOU WERE JAMMIN', LITTLE LADY.

31
00:04:13,019 --> 00:04:16,422
MISS ISUZU! YOUR PLAYING IS
BREATHTAKING AND INSPIRING

32
