LIKE THE GREATEST MUSES OF OLD.

33
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,160
GIVE IT A REST, WILLYA?

34
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:21,928
WE BOTH KNOW I'M
NOT ALL THAT GREAT.

35
00:04:22,028 --> 00:04:24,565
WE JUST ALWAYS HAD INSTRUMENTS
LYING AROUND THE HOUSE,

36
00:04:24,665 --> 00:04:26,399
AND I'D PICK 'EM UP AND PLAY.

37
00:04:26,499 --> 00:04:29,435
YOUR EXQUISITE MELODIES
ENRICHED THE CITY NIGHT!

38
00:04:29,536 --> 00:04:31,505
