44
00:04:43,349 --> 00:04:45,752
I'M GONNA PUNCH YOU
IN YOUR DUMB MOUTH!

45
00:04:45,852 --> 00:04:47,588
[ISUZU] GET BACK HERE
SO I CAN HIT YOU!

46
00:04:47,688 --> 00:04:48,555
[RUDY]
AH! I'M PAYING YOU A COMPLIMENT.

47
00:04:48,655 --> 00:04:49,923
WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU?!

48
00:04:51,391 --> 00:04:53,193
ON A QUEST?

49
00:04:53,293 --> 00:04:54,895
YEAH, TOYA AND
THE OTHER YOUNG ONES

50
00:04:54,995 --> 00:04:56,462
NEED TO GAIN
SOME EXPERIENCE.

51
00:04:56,563 --> 00:04:58,364
