SERARA GO WITH THEM

52
00:04:58,464 --> 00:05:00,266
SO THEY'LL HAVE
ANOTHER HEALER.

53
00:05:00,366 --> 00:05:01,635
IF SHE WANTS TO
GO WITH THEM

54
