WHAT I'D CALL "SUBTLE" EITHER.
SO HERE WE GO.

68
00:05:36,837 --> 00:05:39,706
YEAH, WELL, YOU KNOW.
IT IS THE MAGIC BAG!

69
00:05:39,806 --> 00:05:42,543
