IT'S JUST THE BAG THEY WANT.

71
00:05:45,546 --> 00:05:47,147
THEY'VE BEEN HERE
ALL THIS TIME

72
00:05:47,247 --> 00:05:48,749
AND THEY STILL HAVEN'T HAD
THE CHANCE TO GO OUT AND

73
00:05:48,849 --> 00:05:51,417
COMPLETE ANY OF THE
LARGER QUESTS.

74
00:05:51,518 --> 00:05:53,987
D'YOU... DO YOU THINK
THEY'LL BE OKAY?

75
00:05:54,087 --> 00:05:56,422
YOU MIGHT BE ASKING A LOT.

76
00:05:56,957 --> 00:05:57,824
[BOTH]
HUH?

77
00:05:57,924 --> 00:05:59,492
[MINORI]
EXCUSE ME!

78
00:06:01,762 --> 00:06:03,263
[MINORI] THOUGHT YOU
COULD USE A REFRESHMENT.

79
00:06:03,363 --> 00:06:04,731
WOW! THANK YOU!

80
00:06:04,831 --> 00:06:07,367
SO, YOU'RE ALREADY DONE WITH
YOUR WORK? THAT WAS FAST.

81
00:06:07,467 --> 00:06:09,035
YEAH!

82
00:06:09,135 --> 00:06:12,606
THANKS A LOT. ACTUALLY
THAT WORKS OUT PERFECTLY.

83
00:06:12,706 --> 00:06:14,074
HUH?

84
