00:20:39,873 --> 00:20:41,441
THIS IS GONNA BE SO COOL!

434
00:20:41,542 --> 00:20:43,443
WE'LL BE LIKE
ROCK STARS ON TOUR!

435
00:20:43,544 --> 00:20:44,778
I MEAN WE'LL HAVE TO STOP

436
00:20:44,878 --> 00:20:46,446
AT EVERY VILLAGE FOR WATER
AND SUPPLIES ANYWAY!

437
00:20:46,547 --> 00:20:49,182
UH‐HUH, IF IT'S ALL RIGHT
WITH YOU, SHIROE?

438
00:20:49,282 --> 00:20:50,751
MM‐HM... DEFINITELY.

439
00:20:50,851 --> 00:20:52,986
DON'T GO TRYING ANYTHING
STUPID OUT THERE...

440
00:20:53,086 --> 00:20:54,688
JUST CALL US IF
THINGS GET HAIRY.

441
00:20:54,788 --> 00:20:56,456
WHOA, I THINK
IT WOULD BE BETTER

442
00:20:56,557 --> 00:20:58,892
IF THEY STAYED OFF THE
TELEPATHIC NETWORK.

443
00:20:58,992 --> 00:21:00,561
[ALL] OHHH...?

444
00:21:00,661 --> 00:21:02,663
[NAOTSUGU]
UH... YOU SERIOUS?

445
00:21:02,763 --> 00:21:04,765
IT'S THE POINT OF THEM
GOING OUT ALONE, NAOTSUGU...

446
00:21:04,865 --> 00:21:06,867
THEY NEED TO SOLVE
PROBLEMS ON THEIR OWN.

447
00:21:06,967 --> 00:21:08,702
ALL OF YOU SHOULD THINK
OF THIS WHOLE JOURNEY

448
00:21:08,802 --> 00:21:11,471
AS AN EXTENDED EXERCISE
IN CRITICAL THINKING.

449
00:21:11,572 --> 00:21:13,306
NOT TO MENTION
MEETING NEW PEOPLE,

450
00:21:13,406 --> 00:21:15,308
AND SEEING AND
DOING NEW THINGS.

451
00:21:15,408 --> 00:21:17,511
THAT'S RIGHT! AND YOU
SHOULD DEFINITELY ALLOW ME

452
00:21:17,611 --> 00:21:19,746
TO HANDLE NAVIGATION
AND NEGOTIATIONS!

453
00:21:19,846 --> 00:21:23,950
YEAH! THIS'LL BE A GREAT
EXPERIENCE! WHAT'DYA SAY ISUZU?!

454
00:21:24,050 --> 00:21:25,185
OKAY...

455
00:21:25,285 --> 00:21:28,321
HM? AREN'T YOU EXCITED?

456
00:21:28,421 --> 00:21:29,790
(UNCERTAIN)

457
00:21:29,890 --> 00:21:32,358
UH, SURE...
I'M THRILLED BEYOND WORDS!

458
00:21:32,458 --> 00:21:35,361
I MIGHT HAVE TO GET RUDY HERE
TO FETCH ME SOME EXTRA STRINGS

459
00:21:35,461 --> 00:21:36,597
WHENEVER THEY BREAK ON ME!

460
00:21:36,697 --> 00:21:38,264
(LAUGHTER)
[RUDY] OW, THAT HURTS!

461
00:21:38,364 --> 00:21:39,566
LET GO, MISS ISUZU!
[ISUZU] OH, WHAT'S THE MATTER?

462
00:21:39,666 --> 00:21:41,201
I THOUGHT YOU WERE A MANLY MAN.

463
00:21:41,301 --> 00:21:44,237
YOU SHOULD BE ABLE TO
HANDLE ONE LITTLE BARD.

464
00:21:44,337 --> 00:21:46,673
(HORSES NEIGHING)

465
00:21:49,743 --> 00:21:51,612
[MINORI] AND WE'RE OFF!
[TOYA] WELL WE'RE OFF!

466
00:21:51,712 --> 00:21:54,147
[SERARA] SEE YA LATER!
(LAUGHTER)

467
00:21:54,247 --> 00:21:56,917
(LAUGHTER)

468
00:21:57,017 --> 00:21:59,620
REMEMBER MAINTAINING
YOUR WEAPONS IS CRUCIAL.

469
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:01,421
IF YOU EVER START
FEELING LONELY,

470
00:22:01,522 --> 00:22:03,857
REMEMBER YOU CAN ALWAYS
JUST THINK OF ME!

471
00:22:03,957 --> 00:22:06,259
BE SAFE OUT THERE, HM.

472
00:22:06,359 --> 00:22:10,063
(CRYING)

473
00:22:14,935 --> 00:22:16,670
AHHH!

474
00:22:20,140 --> 00:22:21,608
WE'RE FINALLY DOING IT!

475
00:22:21,708 --> 00:22:23,710
MM‐HM! THERE'S A
LOT OF ROAD AHEAD.

476
00:22:23,810 --> 00:22:25,579
THE START OF OUR WORLD TOUR!

477
00:22:25,679 --> 00:22:28,782
IT'S ADVENTURE TIME!
LET'S DO THIS?!

478
00:22:31,384 --> 00:22:34,621
[MINORI, THINKING]
WELL MASTER SHIROE, HERE I GO!

479
00:22:34,721 --> 00:22:37,524
WITH A BUNCH OF ADVENTURES,
JUST WAITING FOR ME!

480
00:22:37,624 --> 00:22:41,427
[TOYA] LET'S GO! WE'RE HEADED
INTO THE WEST YOU GUYS!

481
00:24:14,921 --> 00:24:16,156
[AKATSUKI, VOICEOVER]
MINORI AND FRIENDS

482
00:24:16,256 --> 00:24:17,891
ARE FULLY ENJOYING
THEIR JOURNEY.

483
00:24:17,991 --> 00:24:20,293
FROM FUN EXPERIENCES
TO DIFFICULT TRIALS,

484
00:24:20,393 --> 00:24:22,195
EVERYTHING ENCOUNTERED
IN THIS NEW WORLD

485
00:24:22,295 --> 00:24:23,730
MAKE THEIR HEARTS DANCE.

486
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:27,467
HOWEVER, THEIR JOURNEY BEGINS
TO FEEL STRANGE AND UNEASY.

487
00:24:27,568 --> 00:24:30,203
A MYSTERIOUS FIGURE
APPEARS BEFORE THEM.

488
00:24:30,303 --> 00:24:34,374
A NEW STRANGER IN GLASSES
GREETS OUR YOUNG ADVENTURERS.

489
00:24:34,474 --> 00:24:37,077
[SHIROE] MY COMRADES
ARE ALWAYS BESIDE ME.

